---
description: SDD lifecycle rule for harness artifacts
globs: AGENTS.md,.agents/**/*.md,specs/**/*.md,progress/**/*.md,reviews/**/*.md
alwaysApply: false
---

Follow the lifecycle `Backlog -> Specification -> Human Approval -> Implementation -> Review -> Human Completion`. Use the templates in `specs/_template/`. Keep requirement IDs stable after review begins. Role contracts in `.agents/*.md` are authoritative; do not duplicate them here.
